reviewText: I ordered it 2 weeks ago from California and I already got it!!!!! I'm surprised it was really fast!!!!! There is no damage on it, every thing is clean and good condition!!!!!

I'm so happy!! I bought this as a replacement for my original copy that no longer worked. I am so impressed with it!! It was a great price for one of my favorite concert dvds. It arrived in great time, was packaged nicely, and in great condition. I am very happy with my purchase and would buy from this seller again in the future.
